### 1. NCU Portal OAuth Login (returns redirect)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/login
###

### 2. Retrieve Authenticated User Profile (Requires Bearer Token)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_APP_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/json
###

